{"title":"复读机 加强版","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["生成函数"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/6696#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=6696","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/6696/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/6696/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/6696"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"见 [UOJ #450. 【集训队作业2018】复读机](http://uoj.ac/problem/450)\r\n\r\n小飞机（<a href=\"https://codeforces.com/profile/ffjet\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><span style=\"color:black\">F</span><span style=\"color:red\">Fjet</span></span></a>）觉得这题的 $d$ 太小了，于是想考考你，能不能做更难的情况？"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行三个正整数 $n, k, d$，意义如题目描述所述。\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行一个正整数，表示方案数对 $19491001$ 取模的值。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入 1\r\n\r\n```plain\r\n8 3 4\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 1\r\n\r\n```plain\r\n213\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入 2\r\n\r\n```plain\r\n12 4 6\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 2\r\n\r\n```plain\r\n5548\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 $50\\%$ 的数据，$d = 4, k\\le 2\\times 10^3$。\r\n\r\n对于另外 $50\\%$ 的数据，$d = 6, k\\le 10^3$。\r\n\r\n对于 $100\\%$ 的数据，保证 $n\\le 10^9$。"}]}